# Force LF line endings on checkout, regardless of the checking-out machine's
# core.autocrlf setting. Without this, a Windows host's git config converts LF->CRLF on
# checkout (including when this repo is pulled in as a submodule), which breaks
# `#!/usr/bin/env bash` shebangs inside the Linux devcontainer (env looks for a program
# literally named "bash\r"). Applies to every consumer that submodules this repo.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh  text eol=lf
